This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, :, To examine the effectiveness of non-hormonal pharmacological treatments for relieving hot flushes in postmenopausal women., In separate comparisons, we will assess non-hormonal treatments for their effectiveness in the relief of hot flushes:, Non-hormonal treatments versus placebo, Non-hormonal treatments versus hormonal replacement therapy, Non-hormonal treatments versus no-treatment control group, :, To determine the adverse effects of non-hormonal treatments., To evaluate the impact on quality of life of non-hormonal treatments versus no-treatment control, placebo or hormonal replacement therapy